  "title": "Cleaning Supervisor",
  "description": "<p>1. Supervise multiple teams of cleaners in multiple cleaning projects while ensuring service quality delivery and safety.</p>\n<p>2. Assist in the planning of cleaning service operations work plans, incident management, and managing inventory of the cleaning equipment and materials used in multiple project sites.</p>\n<p>3. Provide guidance to the cleaners.</p>\n<p>4. Communicate with stakeholders.</p>\n<p>5. Able to multi-task.</p>\n<p>6. Monitor and manage cleaning services and teams</p>\n<p>7. Ensure adherence to safety measures during cleaning operations.</p>\n<p>8. Submit cleaning reports to management.</p>\n<p>9. Manage inventory, equipment, and maintenance schedule</p>\n<p>Manage cleaning related incidents</p>",
